    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;"><a href="http://www.cs.cmu.edu/~ninamf/courses/601sp15/index.html" target="_self">Machine Learning</a> (Tom Mitchell/Carnegie Mellon University): Carnegie Mellon’s graduate introductory machine learning course. A prerequisite to their second graduate level course, “Statistical Machine Learning.” Taped university lectures with practice problems, homework assignments, and a midterm (all with solutions) posted online. A <a href="http://www.cs.cmu.edu/~tom/10701_sp11/" target="_self">2011 version</a> of the course also exists. CMU is one of the best graduate schools for studying machine learning and has a whole department dedicated to ML. Free.</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
